(2201, 119, 'artist_bio', 'Freya has exhibited in galleries, completed permanent and ephemeral commissions in public space around Australia and internationally. Recently Freya has covered a tram for the Melbourne Art Tram project, shown work at the Gertrude St Projection Festival and participated in Skypetrait; transcontinental faces, a research project between Melbourne and Reutlingen University in Germany. Using projection to explore ways of interrupting the experience of space and self and encourage reflexive engagement, she is currently completing her Masters of Art in Public Space at RMIT University.'),
