(153, 3, '2013-11-26 03:51:24', '2013-11-26 03:51:24', '<i>Midden </i>has been commissioned by White Night Melbourne for Birrarung Marr. Real-time 3D content visualisations created by ENESS, an award winning art and design practice based in Melbourne, will respond to the dynamic ambient soundscape. An illuminating 360 degree projection will be mapped onto a 150 cubic metre mound of rocks. <i>Midden</i> pays homage to the traditional owners of the land.  This powerful, collaborative work expresses the interplay of Australian culture and creativity.', 'Midden', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'midden', '', '', '2013-11-26 03:51:24', '2013-11-26 03:51:24', '', 0, 'http://whitenight.dev/?post_type=event&#038;p=153', 0, 'event', '', 0),
