(155, 3, '2013-11-26 03:51:24', '2013-11-26 03:51:24', '<i>Crepuscular Beam</i> is a large collection of searchlights staged in the centre of Melbourne. These roving, penetrating light forces will sweep the city providing a visual beacon that highlight central hubs of activity throughout the darkened hours of the night. The audience will be able to engage with the work from afar as the beams reach for kilometres into the night sky and also, up close, experience the lights morphing accompanied by an emotive soundtrack.', 'Crepuscular Beam', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'crepuscular-beam', '', '', '2013-11-26 04:11:33', '2013-11-26 04:11:33', '', 0, 'http://whitenight.dev/?post_type=event&#038;p=155', 0, 'event', '', 0),
